The paper deals with scheduling problems, which are typically studied in the algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) sub-category. However, the paper also considers metrics related to information theory (cs.IT) and fairness (cs.LG), as well as the use of multiple processors (cs.SY) and optimization (cs.PF).
